                        <p>手續費的計算方式為你的 Jetpack 方案所適用的比例乘上收益金額。免費方案為 10%，Creator 方案則為 2% (Stripe 手續費另計)。</p>','Transaction fees'=>'交易手續費','Unlimited subscribers'=>'無限制訂閱者','100 subscribers'=>'100 名訂閱者','Import a CSV file of your existing subscribers to be sent your Newsletter.'=>'匯入現有訂閱者的 CSV 檔案來寄送電子報。','Import subscribers'=>'匯入訂閱者','Monetize your online presence and earn from your website'=>'用你的線上知名度獲益，從網站賺取收入','Grow your subscribers through our creator network and tools'=>'運用我們的創作者網路和工具增加訂閱者','Create content that stands out'=>'打造不同凡響的內容','product name shown in menuJetpack Manage'=>'Jetpack Manage','Jetpack Manage'=>'Jetpack Manage','IP address `%1$s` just failed is_usable_domain check as it is in the private network.'=>'IP 位址「%1$s」未通過 is_usable_domain 檢查，因為該位址位於私密網路。','Generate text, tables, lists, and forms'=>'產生文字、表格、清單和表單','Unable to save new URL secret'=>'無法儲存新的 URL 密鑰','You do not have the correct user permissions to perform this action.'=>'你沒有正確的使用者權限可執行此動作。','URL secret does not exist.'=>'URL 密鑰不存在。','Upgrade'=>'升級','Priority support'=>'優先支援服務','Included'=>'包含','Severity labels'=>'嚴重程度標籤','Notifications'=>'通知','One-click auto fixes'=>'一鍵自動修正','Access to scan on Cloud'=>'存取雲端掃瞄','Brute force protection'=>'防護暴力密碼破解攻擊','Automatic protection and rule updates'=>'自動防護和規則更新','Manual rules only'=>'僅限手動規則','Web Application Firewall'=>'網頁應用程式防火牆','Plus on-demand manual scans'=>'加上隨選即用手動掃瞄','Daily automated scans'=>'日常自動掃瞄','Line by line malware scanning'=>'惡意軟體逐行掃瞄','Check items against database'=>'比對資料庫來檢查項目','Scan for threats and vulnerabilities'=>'掃瞄威脅和漏洞','Generate text, tables, and lists'=>'產生文字、表格和清單','Jetpack AI Assistant brings the power of AI right into your WordPress editor, letting your content creation soar to new heights.'=>'Jetpack AI 助理可將 AI 功能直接整合進 WordPress 編輯器，讓你的內容創作邁向全新境界。','<p>Paid customers get dedicated email support from our world-class Happiness Engineers to help with any issue.</p>
						 <p>All other questions are handled by our team as quickly as we are able to go through the WordPress support forum.</p>'=>'<p>付費客戶的任何問題，都會由我們的世界級 Happiness Engineer 透過專屬電子郵件支援提供協助。</p>
						 <p>其他所有問題都會由我們的團隊透過 WordPress.com 支援論壇盡快處理。</p>','Dedicated email support'=>'專屬電子郵件支援','Deliver images from Jetpack\'s Content Delivery Network. Automatically resizes your images to an appropriate size, converts them to modern efficient formats like WebP, and serves them from a worldwide network of servers.'=>'透過 Jetpack 內容傳遞網路顯示圖片。 自動將圖片調整至適當大小、將圖片轉換為現代高效率格式 (例如 WebP)，並透過遍及全球的伺服器網路顯示圖片。','Image CDN'=>'圖片 CDN','Discover and fix images with a suboptimal resolution, aspect ratio, or file size, improving user experience and page speed.'=>'發現並修正圖片不夠理想的解析度、長寬比或檔案大小，改善使用者體驗和頁面速度。','Image guide'=>'圖片指南','Run non-essential JavaScript after the page has loaded so that styles and images can load more quickly.'=>'在頁面載入後再執行非必要的 JavaScript，加快樣式和圖片的載入速度。','Defer non-essential JavaScript'=>'延遲非必要的 JavaScript','<p>It’s essential to regenerate Critical CSS to optimize your site speed whenever your HTML or CSS structure changes. Being on top of this can be tedious and time-consuming.</p>
								 <p>Boost’s cloud service can automatically detect when your site needs the Critical CSS regenerated, and perform this function behind the scenes without requiring you to monitor it manually.</p>'=>'<p>重新產生關鍵 CSS 至關重要，這可讓你在 HTML 或 CSS 架構變更時享有最佳網站速度。 這些事務處理起來可能十分繁複且費時。</p>
								 <p>Boost 的雲端服務可自動偵測你的網站何時需要重新產生關鍵 CSS，不必手動監控就能在背景中執行此功能。</p>','Automatic Critical CSS regeneration'=>'自動重新產生關鍵 CSS','<p>To enhance the speed of your site, with this plan you will need to optimize CSS by using the Manual Critical CSS generation feature whenever you:</p>
								<ul>
									<li>Make theme changes.</li>
									<li>Write a new post/page.</li>
									<li>Edit a post/page.</li>
									<li>Activate, deactivate, or update plugins that impact your site layout or HTML structure.</li>
									<li>Change settings of plugins that impact your site layout or HTML structure.</li>
									<li>Upgrade your WordPress version if the new release includes core CSS changes.</li>
								</ul>'=>'<p>為加快你的網站速度，在使用此方案的情況下，每當你執行下列操作時，就需要使用手動產生關鍵 CSS 功能來最佳化 CSS：</p>
								<ul>
									<li>變更佈景主題。</li>
									<li>撰寫新文章/頁面。</li>
									<li>編輯文章/頁面。</li>
									<li>啟用、停用或更新會影響網站版面配置或 HTML 架構的外掛程式。</li>
									<li>變更會影響網站版面配置或 HTML 架構的外掛程式設定。</li>
									<li>升級包含核心 CSS 變更的 WordPress 新版本。</li>
								</ul>','Manual Critical CSS regeneration'=>'手動重新產生關鍵 CSS','Move important styling information to the start of the page, which helps pages display your content sooner, so your users don’t have to wait for the entire page to load. Commonly referred to as Critical CSS.'=>'將重要樣式資訊移至頁面開頭，這有助於加快頁面顯示內容的速度，讓使用者不必等待系統載入整個頁面。 通常稱為關鍵 CSS。','Starter Product FeatureComment & form spam protection'=>'留言與表單的垃圾訊息防護功能','Starter Product FeatureOne-click fixes for most threats'=>'一鍵修復多數威脅','Starter Product FeatureReal-time cloud backups with 1GB storage'=>'即時雲端備份功能，享有 1GB 儲存空間','Essential security tools: real-time backups and comment spam protection.'=>'必備安全工具：即時備份和垃圾留言防護功能。','Something went wrong. Please try again.'=>'發生錯誤。 請再試一次。','Sorry, something is wrong with your Jetpack connection.'=>'很抱歉，你的 Jetpack 連結發生問題。','Comprehensive site security, including VaultPress Backup, Scan, and Akismet Anti-spam.'=>'為網站提供全方位的安全保障，包括 VaultPress Backup、Scan 和 Akismet Anti-Spam。','Akismet Anti-spam'=>'Akismet Anti-Spam','Jetpack VaultPress Backup'=>'Jetpack VaultPress Backup','Backup Product DisclaimerLearn more'=>'瞭解詳情','Backup Product Disclaimer* Subject to your usage and storage limit.'=>'* 視你的使用方式和儲存空間限制而定。','As always, feel free to <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact our support team</a> if you have any questions.'=>'一如往常，若有任何問題，歡迎<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">聯絡我們的支援團隊</a>。','<a href=\'%s\' target=\'_blank\' rel=\'noopener noreferrer\'>Learn more</a> about the connection owner and what will break if you do not have one.'=>'<a href=\'%s\' target=\'_blank\' rel=\'noopener noreferrer\'>深入瞭解</a>連線擁有者，以及沒有連線擁有者會造成什麼問題。','Connect to WordPress.com'=>'連結 WordPress.com','Every Jetpack site needs at least one connected admin for the features to work properly. Please connect to your WordPress.com account via the button below. Once you connect, you may refresh this page to see an option to change the connection owner.'=>'所有 Jetpack 網站皆需至少設置一名連結管理員，網站功能才能正常運作。 請透過下方按鈕連結至你的 WordPress.com 帳號。 連結完成後，請重新整理此頁面，你就會看到變更連結擁有者的選項。','Success!'=>'成功！','Set new connection owner'=>'設定新的連結擁有者','You can choose to transfer connection ownership to one of these already-connected admins:'=>'你可以選擇將連結所有權轉移給以下任一位已連結的管理員：','Warning! You are about to delete the Jetpack connection owner (%s) for this site, which may cause some of your Jetpack features to stop working.'=>'警告！ 你即將刪除此網站的 Jetpack 連線擁有者 (%s)，這可能導致部分 Jetpack 功能停止運作。','Important notice about your Jetpack connection:'=>'關於 Jetpack 連結的重要通知：','New free service: Show Canada Post shipping rates on your store!'=>'全新免費服務：在商店顯示加拿大郵政 (Canada Post) 的送貨費率！','New free service: Show USPS shipping rates on your store! Added bonus: print shipping labels without leaving WooCommerce.'=>'全新免費服務：在商店顯示美國郵政服務 (USPS) 的送貨費率！新增的獎勵：無需離開 WooCommerce 即可列印送貨標籤。','Activating'=>'啟用中','Activated'=>'已啟用','Supports the major social networks'=>'支援主要的社群網路','Schedule publishing'=>'排程發表','Post to social networks'=>'張貼至社群網路','An unknown error occurred during installation'=>'安裝過程中發生不明錯誤','There was an error installing your plugin'=>'安裝外掛程式時發生錯誤','You are not allowed to install plugins on this site.'=>'你不得在此網站安裝外掛程式。','Scan Product FeatureAccess to latest Firewall rules'=>'存取最新防火牆規則','Easy to navigate and use'=>'可輕鬆導覽和使用','Check plugin and theme version status'=>'檢查外掛程式和佈景主題版本狀態','Daily automatic scans'=>'每日自動掃描','Over 20,000 listed vulnerabilities'=>'超過 20,000 個列出的漏洞','My Jetpack dashboard'=>'我的 Jetpack 儀表板','The following Jetpack licenses are invalid, already in use, or revoked: %s'=>'以下 Jetpack 授權無效、已在使用中或已撤銷：%s','Failed to attach your Jetpack license(s). Please try reconnecting Jetpack.'=>'無法附加你的 Jetpack 授權。 請嘗試重新連結 Jetpack。','License attach request failed.'=>'授權附加要求失敗。','Jetpack doesn\'t have a connected owner.'=>'Jetpack 沒有連線的擁有者。','Missing parameter "last_detached_count".'=>'遺失參數「last_detached_count」','Could not set this license key. Please try again.'=>'無法設定此授權金鑰。 請再試一次。','%s must be a non-negative integer.'=>'%s 須為非負整數。','%s must be a string.'=>'%s 必須是字串。','Activate'=>'啟用','VideoPress Product FeatureUnlimited users'=>'不限使用者人數','VideoPress Product FeatureAd-free and customizable player'=>'不含廣告且可自訂的播放器','VideoPress Product FeatureBuilt into WordPress editor'=>'WordPress 編輯器內建','VideoPress Product Feature1TB of storage'=>'1TB 儲存空間','Security Product FeatureComment & form spam protection'=>'留言與表單的垃圾訊息防護功能','Security Product FeatureOne-click fixes for most threats'=>'一鍵修復多數威脅','Security Product FeatureAutomated real-time malware scan'=>'自動即時掃瞄惡意軟體','Security Product FeatureReal-time cloud backups with 10GB storage'=>'即時雲端備份功能，享有 10GB 儲存空間','Spelling correction'=>'拼字更正','Supports 38 languages'=>'支援 38 種語言','Powerful filtering'=>'強化過濾功能','Instant search and indexing'=>'即時搜尋與編目','Help your site visitors find answers instantly so they keep reading and buying. Great for sites with a lot of content.'=>'讓訪客立即找到想要的資訊，確保留存、提高購買轉換率。 非常適合內含大量內容的網站。','Scan Product FeatureInstant email notifications'=>'即時電子郵件通知','Scan Product FeatureOne-click fixes for most issues'=>'單鍵修復多數問題','Scan Product FeatureAutomated daily scanning'=>'每日自動掃瞄','Automatic scanning and one-click fixes keep your site one step ahead of security threats and malware.'=>'自動掃瞄和單鍵修復功能，讓你的網站能夠預防資安威脅和惡意軟體。','You are not allowed to activate plugins on this site.'=>'你不得在此網站啟用外掛程式。','Error activating Jetpack module'=>'啟用 Jetpack 模組時發生錯誤','Error activating Jetpack plugin'=>'啟用 Jetpack 外掛程式時發生錯誤','Activation failed. Plugin is not installed'=>'啟用失敗。 未安裝外掛程式','Basic tools for a successful site'=>'打造成功網站的基礎工具','Infinitely customizable with integrations and extensions'=>'利用整合服務和擴充功能自訂，不受限制','Fully integrated with WordPress & WooCommerce'=>'與 WordPress 和 WooCommerce 完全整合','Manage billing and create invoices'=>'管理帳單與建立報價票','Manage unlimited contacts'=>'管理不限人數的聯絡人','Standalone free plugin for those focused on speed'=>'提供獨立免費外掛程式，想加速就來用','Enable improvements in one click'=>'單鍵啟用強化功能','Check your site performance'=>'檢視網站效能','Backup Product FeatureOne-click restores'=>'一鍵還原','Backup Product Feature30-day archive & activity log*'=>'30 天彙整和活動記錄*','Backup Product Feature10GB of backup storage'=>'10GB 備份儲存空間','Backup Product FeatureReal-time cloud backups'=>'即時雲端備份','Never lose a word, image, page, or time worrying about your site with automated backups & one-click restores.'=>'使用自動備份和一鍵還原功能，再也不必擔心網站損失任何文字、圖像、頁面。','Anti-Spam Product FeatureAdvanced stats'=>'進階統計資料','Anti-Spam Product FeatureBlock spam without CAPTCHAs'=>'不需要輸入 Captcha 也能阻擋垃圾訊息','Anti-Spam Product FeatureComment and form spam protection'=>'留言與表單的垃圾訊息防護功能','Save time and get better responses by automatically blocking spam from your comments and forms.'=>'自動攔阻留言和表單中的垃圾訊息，讓你節省大量時間，與訪客互動更加順暢。','Unable to fetch the products list from WordPress.com'=>'無法從 WordPress.com 擷取產品清單','Your site is not connected to Jetpack.'=>'此網站未與 Jetpack 連結。','The product argument must be a string.'=>'產品引數必須為字串。','Production action to execute'=>'要執行的生產動作','Product slug'=>'商品動態網址','Enhance your site with dozens of other features'=>'利用各項功能增強網站','Get notifications if your site goes offline'=>'在網站離線時收到通知','Protect your site against bot attacks'=>'保護網站不被 Bot 攻擊','Speed up your site with optimized images'=>'利用最佳化圖片提升網站速度','Secure and speed up your site for free with Jetpack\'s powerful WordPress tools.'=>'使用 Jetpack 強大的 WordPress 工具，免費保護網站並提升速度。','Unable to fetch the requested data.'=>'無法擷取要求的資料。','No valid event name or type.'=>'無有效的事件名稱或類型。','You aren’t authorized to do that.'=>'你沒有權限進行此操作。','Unknown Plugin Update Failure'=>'未知外掛程式更新錯誤','Do we want the checksum or object ids.'=>'需要總和檢查碼還是物件 ID。','Shared Salt to use when generating checksum'=>'產生總和檢查碼時使用的分享鹽','Strip non-ascii characters?'=>'移除非 ASCII 字元？','End ID for the histogram'=>'長條圖的結束 ID','Start ID for the histogram'=>'長條圖的開始 ID','Number of histogram buckets.'=>'長條圖貯體的數量。','Column mappings'=>'欄位對應','If text fields should be converted to latin1 in checksum calculation.'=>'總和檢查碼計算文字欄位是否應轉換為 latin1。','Size of batches'=>'批次大小','Name of Sync module.'=>'同步模組名稱。','Name of Sync queue.'=>'同步佇列名稱。','Objects Identifiers'=>'物件識別碼','Object Type'=>'物件類型','Name of Sync module'=>'同步模組名稱','New Sync health status'=>'新同步健康狀態','Comment IDs to include in Full Sync'=>'要包含在完整同步中的留言 ID','Post IDs to include in Full Sync'=>'要包含在完整同步中的文章 ID','User IDs to include in Full Sync or "initial"'=>'要包含在完整同步或「初始」中的使用者 ID','Data Modules that should be included in Full Sync'=>'應包含在完整同步中的資料模組','UTC%s'=>'UTC%s','Every %d minutes'=>'每 %d 分鐘','Sync has been blocked from WordPress.com because it would cause an identity crisis'=>'WordPress.com 已封鎖同步功能，因為它可能會導致身分危機','Sync has been aborted because the IXR client is missing.'=>'由於 IXR 用戶端遺失，因此已中止同步。','Your password is too weak: Looks like you are including easy to guess information about yourself. Try something a little more unique.'=>'你的密碼太過簡單：密碼似乎包含你的個人資訊，容易被人猜到。 請嘗試使用較為獨特的密碼。','This is a very common password. Choose something that will be harder for others to guess.'=>'這是十分常見的密碼。選擇其他人難以猜測的密碼。','This password is too easy to guess: you can improve it by including special characters such as !#=?*&.'=>'這個密碼強度不足，極易猜測：你可以混合使用特殊字元 (例如 !#=?*&)，以提高密碼的強度。','This password is too easy to guess: you can improve it by mixing both letters and numbers.'=>'這個密碼強度不足，極易猜測：你可以混合使用字母和數字，提高密碼的強度。','This password is too easy to guess: you can improve it by adding additional uppercase letters, lowercase letters, or numbers.'=>'這個密碼強度不足，極易猜測：你可以透過新增其他的大小寫字母或數字，提升密碼強度。','Password must be at least %d characters.'=>'密碼至少要有 %d 個字元。','Passwords may not contain the character "\\".'=>'密碼不能含有字元「\\」。','My Jetpack'=>'我的 Jetpack','Could not confirm migration.'=>'無法確認遷移。','Could not delete sync error option.'=>'無法刪除同步錯誤選項。','Could not confirm safe mode.'=>'無法確認安全模式。','Cannot parse URL %s'=>'無法貼上 URL %s','Jetpack Safe Mode'=>'Jetpack 安全模式','Last heartbeat sent at: %s'=>'上次活動訊號傳送時間： %s','%s is not a valid command.'=>'%s 不是有效的命令。','Invalid blog token'=>'網誌權杖無效','Invalid token for user %d'=>'使用者權杖無效 %d','No blog token found'=>'找不到網誌權杖','Requesting user_id %1$d does not match token user_id %2$d'=>'請求的 user_id %1$d 與權杖 user_id %2$d 不符','Token for user %d is malformed'=>'使用者權杖 %d 格式錯誤','No token for user %d'=>'沒有使用者權杖 %d','No primary user defined'=>'未定義主意少用者','No user tokens found'=>'找不到使用者權杖','You need to register your Jetpack before connecting it.'=>'你需要註冊才連接 Jetpack。','An administrator for this blog must set up the Jetpack connection.'=>'你必須設定連接 Jetpack 的網站管理員。','Secret mismatch'=>'密碼不符','Verification secrets are incomplete'=>'驗證密碼不完整','Verification secrets are empty'=>'驗證密碼空白','Verification took too long'=>'驗證花費太長時間','Verification secrets not found'=>'找不到驗證密碼','The required "%s" parameter is malformed.'=>'要求的「%s」參數格式錯誤。','The required "%s" parameter is missing.'=>'要求的「%s」參數遺失。','Failed to disconnect the site as it appears already disconnected.'=>'無法中斷連結此網站，因為網站似乎已中斷連結。','Site is not connected'=>'網站未連線','Invalid user id is provided'=>'提供的使用者 ID 無效','Invalid user token is provided'=>'提供的使用者權杖無效','New owner'=>'新增擁有者','Is connection owner'=>'是連線擁有者','New user token'=>'新增使用者權杖','Indicates from what plugin the request is coming from'=>'顯示該要求來自哪個外掛程式','URI of the admin page where the user should be redirected after connection flow'=>'連線流程後，使用者應重新導向的管理員頁面 URI','Indicates where the registration action was triggered for tracking/segmentation purposes'=>'表示觸發註冊動作的位置，以用於追蹤/區隔用途','The isActive argument should be set to false.'=>'isActive 引數應設為 false。','Set to false will trigger the site to disconnect.'=>'設為 false 將觸發網站中斷連結。','You do not have the correct user permissions to perform this action.
			Please contact your site admin if you think this is a mistake.'=>'你沒有正確的使用者權限可執行此動作。
			如果你認為有錯誤，請聯絡你的網站管理員。','The request is not signed correctly.'=>'要求並未正確簽署。','This request method does not support body parameters.'=>'此要求方法並不支援本文參數。','This request method is not supported.'=>'並未支援此要求方法。','The request method is missing.'=>'缺少請求方法。','You cannot call this method until Jetpack Config is configured'=>'設定 Jetpack Config 之前，你無法叫用此方法','Error Details: %s'=>'錯誤詳細信息：%s','The Client ID/WP.com Blog ID of this site'=>'此網站客戶端的 ID 帳號 / WP.com 的部落格 ID 帳號。','Jetpack Plugin Version'=>'Jetpack 外掛版本','The number of sites of the connected WP.com user'=>'已連結的 WP.com 使用者的網站數量','The WP.com user email of the connected user'=>'已連結的使用者的 WP.com 使用者電子郵件','The WP.com username of the connected user'=>'已連結的使用者的 WP.com 使用者名稱','The WP.com user ID of the connected user'=>'已連結的使用者的 WP.com 使用者 ID','Domain `%1$s` just failed is_usable_domain check as it is a subdomain of WordPress.com.'=>'網域「%1$s」未通過 is_usable_domain 檢查，因為該網域為 WordPress.com 的子網域。','Domain `%1$s` just failed is_usable_domain check as it uses an invalid top level domain.'=>'網域「%1$s」未通過 is_usable_domain 檢查，因為該網域使用無效的頂層網域。','Domain `%1$s` just failed is_usable_domain check as it is in the forbidden array.'=>'網域「%1$s」未通過 is_usable_domain 檢查，因為該網域位於禁止的 array 中。','Domain `%1$s` just failed is_usable_domain check as it is empty.'=>'網域「%1$s」未通過 is_usable_domain 檢查，因為該網域為空白。','Invalid Registration State'=>'註冊狀態無效','Error Details: Jetpack ID begins with a numeral. Do not publicly post this error message! %s'=>'錯誤詳細資料：Jetpack ID 以數字為開頭。請勿公開發表此錯誤訊息！%s','Error Details: Jetpack ID is not a scalar. Do not publicly post this error message! %s'=>'錯誤詳細資料：Jetpack ID 並非純量。請勿公開發表此錯誤訊息！%s','Error Details: Jetpack ID is empty. Do not publicly post this error message! %s'=>'錯誤詳細資料：Jetpack ID 為空白。請勿公開發表此錯誤訊息！%s','PHP\'s XML extension is not available. Jetpack requires the XML extension to communicate with WordPress.com. Please contact your hosting provider to enable PHP\'s XML extension.'=>'PHP 的 XML 延伸模組無法使用。Jetpack 需要 XML 延伸模組才能與 WordPress.com 通訊。請聯絡您的主機服務提供者以啟用 PHP 的 XML 延伸模組。','Jetpack experienced an issue trying to save options (cannot_save_secrets). We suggest that you contact your hosting provider, and ask them for help checking that the options table is writable on your site.'=>'Jetpack 嘗試儲存選項時遇到問題 (cannot_save_secrets)。 建議你與託管服務提供者聯絡，請他們檢查網站的選項表格是否可寫入。','Could not confirm new owner.'=>'無法確認新的擁有者。','New owner is not connected'=>'新的擁有者未連線','New owner is same as existing owner'=>'新的擁有者與現有擁有者相同','New owner is not admin'=>'新的擁有者不是管理員','Your connection with WordPress.com seems to be broken. If you\'re experiencing issues, please try reconnecting.'=>'你與 WordPress.com 的連線似乎已中斷。 若你遇到問題，請嘗試重新連線。','The required "local_user" parameter is missing.'=>'要求的「local_user」參數遺失。','Failed to fetch user token from WordPress.com.'=>'無法從 WordPress.com 擷取使用者權杖。','A non-empty nonce must be supplied.'=>'必須提供非空白隨機數。','Valid user is required.'=>'需要有效的使用者。','Jetpack is already connected.'=>'Jetpack 已連結。','Blog is already registered'=>'網誌已註冊','There was an unspecified error registering the site'=>'註冊網站時發生不明錯誤','There was an issue validating this request.'=>'驗證此要求發生問題。','The required "nonce" parameter is missing.'=>'要求的「nonce」參數遺失。','Valid user is required'=>'需要有效的使用者','User not found.'=>'找不到使用者。','Invalid user identifier.'=>'無效的使用者識別碼。','Unable to load class %1$s. Please add the package that contains it using composer and make sure you are requiring the Jetpack autoloader'=>'無法載入類別 %1$s。 請使用編輯器新增包含它的套件，並確認你要求的是 Jetpack Autoloader','User not found'=>'找不到使用者','Term not found'=>'找不到字詞','Post not found'=>'找不到文章','Comment not found'=>'找不到留言','Object not found'=>'找不到物件','Helper script body must be base64 encoded'=>'小幫手指令碼主體必須為 Base64 編碼','You are not allowed to perform this action.'=>'你無權執行此操作。','The name argument should be an option name or an array of option names'=>'名稱引數應該是選項名稱或選項名稱陣列','One or more option names to include in the backup'=>'要包含在備份中的一個或多個選項名稱','ID of the database object to fetch'=>'要擷取的資料庫物件 ID','The object_type argument should be one of %s'=>'object_type 引數應為 %s 之一','The object_type argument must be a non-empty string.'=>'object_type 引數必須是非空白的字串。','Type of object to fetch from the database'=>'從資料庫擷取的物件類型','Path to Backup Helper Script'=>'備份協助程式指令碼路徑','base64 encoded Backup Helper Script body.'=>'備份協助程式指令碼主體使用 base64 編碼。','Textdomain aliases should be registered before the %1$s hook. This notice was triggered by the %2$s domain.'=>'Textdomain 別名應於 %1$s 勾點前註冊。 %2$s 網域已觸發此通知。','Script "%s" depends on wp-i18n but does not specify "textdomain"'=>'指令碼「%s」視 wp-i18n 而定，但不指定「textdomain」','Settings'=>'設定','https://jetpack.com/'=>'https://jetpack.com/','Easily restore or download a backup of your site from a specific moment in time.'=>'輕鬆還原或下載這個網站指定時間的備份。','https://jetpack.com/jetpack-backup'=>'https://jetpack.com/jetpack-backup']];